<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Documento</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/c9/informeMoroso.css">
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">

  <!-- Activa el dark mode-->
</head>

<body>
  <div id="elemento">
    <div id="encabezado">
      <h1 id="titulo">LPP Concesionaria de Autos</h1>
      <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="logo" height="100px">
      <img src="/img/logoLPP.png" alt="logo" height="100px">
    </div>
    <ol>
      <div>
        <div>Informe de Moroso.</div>
        NRO.: <br>
        <%=data.codMOR%><br><br>
          <div>Refiere al préstamo</div>
          NRO.: <br>
          <%=data.codPRE%><br><br>
            Fecha: <br>
            <%=data.fecha%><br><br>
              <div> Hacemos constancia a través de este informe de que el CLIENTE: <%=data.labelCliente%> cuyo
                  documento es <%=data.labelDoc%> adeuda <%=data.cant%> cuotas del préstamo,
                      sumando un total de
                      $<%=data.montoDeuda%> adeudados. Esto corresponde a la compra del automóvil
                        <%=data.labelAuto%>.Por este motivo se lo ha declarado como un cliente
                          moroso. Se iniciarán las acciones de judicialización en la brevedad.
              </div>
      </div>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <br><br>
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <button id="printButton" class="btn btn-danger">Imprimir o Descargar</button>
    <a href="/c9" class="btn btn-danger ">Finalizar Operacion</a>
  </div>
  <style>
    #elemento {
      width: 210mm !important;
      margin-top: 80px !important;
      height: 297mm !important;
      background: white !important;
      border-radius: 5px !important;
      border: 0px !important;
      font-size: 20px !important;
      padding-left: 0 !important
    }


    #printButton,
    #finalizar {
      opacity: 1 !important;
      border: 2px solid black !important;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center !important;
      margin: 40px !important;
      border: 2px solid black !important;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: black;
      color: white !important;
      font-size: 20px !important;
      font-family: sans-serif !important;
      text-decoration: none !important;
      cursor: pointer !important;
    }

    #logo {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      width: 150px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      margin-left: 20px !important;
    }

    #titulo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 0px;
      margin-bottom: -20px;
      font-family: calibri, monospace;
      font-size: 22px !important;
      font-weight: bold !important;
    }

    @page {
      size: A4;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #e0e0e0 !important;
    }

    #otroElemento {
      padding: 0px !important;
    }
  </style>
  <script>
    function printOrDownload() {
      window.print();
    }
    document.getElementById('printButton').addEventListener('click', printOrDownload);
  </script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>